    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but can you get more specific? Like, if a judge had to decide between a suspended sentence with probation for Profile A versus a short term of actual jail time for Profile B, how would the mitigating/aggravating factors play out? Why would one be more suited for rehab and the other for punishment?",
